{"tid":1963300,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"旺角舖位空置率高達20%創新高    料數以千計食肆倒閉","createTime":"2020-04-08T04:53:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T07:22:26.000Z","uid":79563,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a646724484bf7cb8f20b637d65447d96ba99f24c","tid":1963300,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T04:53:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JgGZQcFhnQOMPUBPNPy.pQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTAyNDtoPTUwMA--/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-04/97c748e0-7543-11ea-bcd9-4b84424516f9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FJgGZQcFhnQOMPUBPNPy.pQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTAyNDtoPTUwMA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-04%2F97c748e0-7543-11ea-bcd9-4b84424516f9&h=ab199a04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情為本港經濟帶來了前所未有的衝擊，嚴重打擊市民消費意欲，零售市場在未來幾個月的日子仍然會相當艱難。有資料顯示，四大核心區主要街道舖位空置率全面上升，其中旺角首季舖位空置率高達20%，創歷來新高，較去年同期高出14.5個百分點，中環吉舖情況同樣嚴重，首季空置率高達14.2%，有專家預計未來將有數以千計的食肆倒閉；調查亦都指出，零售行業超過四成預計將於今年削減人手；另一方面，有消息指，港府最快今日下午，公布第二輪防疫抗疫基金詳情，支援疫情期間受影響行業。<br />\n<br />\n東方：旺角舖兩成空置歷來最高<br />\n信報：零售業逾四成今年擬削人手 畢馬威：反映去歲社會事件損招聘意欲"},{"pid":"7c0fdf16209ba8b378146435d8fb09c8d91d7e1d","tid":1963300,"uid":200070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T04:55:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />攬炒"},{"pid":"c122d3241dcba45141130b619cf1a84d8d4975cf","tid":1963300,"uid":200070,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7c0fdf16209ba8b378146435d8fb09c8d91d7e1d","tid":1963300,"uid":200070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T04:55:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.p