00,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T05:49:54.000Z","msg":"要怪就怪業主"},{"pid":"6ce00d8d0494e6914dd44b7f9544f4214ab942bd","tid":1963300,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dadf921e926cbf85b61573f9e8c31f980cecab74","tid":1963300,"uid":123615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T05:40:51.000Z","msg":"地產霸權肯減租<br />\nD鋪咪唔會吉囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T06:12:18.000Z","msg":"業主劈價50%都唔會減租<br />\n五大訴求定業主減租會實現先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中環卑利街舖4年勁蝕逾千萬   業主劈價幅度達50%</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4fTWX02X.Vaf8CdFDaYbRA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-04/e0ea6210-785d-11ea-b6df-527463447171\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F4fTWX02X.Vaf8CdFDaYbRA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-04%2Fe0ea6210-785d-11ea-b6df-527463447171&h=3ce2e036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n零售市道慘淡，舖位身價大跌，於高位接貨的投資者更要損手離場。中環卑利街一個地舖，原業主於2015年11月以2400萬元承接，剛以1500萬元沽出，持貨逾4年賬面虧損900萬元（37.5%），計及印花稅及代理佣金等開支，料勁蝕超過1140萬元。<br />\n<br />\n消息指出，中環卑利街18A至18B號福志樓地下4號舖，建築面積420方呎，去年起一直以3000萬元叫價放售，惟今年初受新冠肺炎疫情影響，2月已把意向價調低至2400萬元，最終更僅以1500萬元沽出，劈價幅度達50%，呎價約3.57萬元。舖位現由粉麵廠承租，月租3萬元，回報約2.4厘。<br />\n<br />\n代理指出，原業主當日買入該舖位是看好有關地段具收購潛力，但近年一直未見有任何收購活動，加上市況逆轉，決心蝕讓離場。"},{"pid":"d1e0f10a11c75ec9cb61ee733abefdf2b6711259","tid":1963300,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T06:13:01.000Z","msg":"執囉"},{"pid":"dae49f27f694e4f2c807f04bd73ceda2dffade99","tid":1963300,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T06:16:50.000Z","msg":"20%唔夠囉, 我要50%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5564822bcb4731604b0216a8bf3021a4b8aa2d0d","tid":1963300,"uid":72630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T06:17:28.000Z","msg":"無5成唔好囉出黎講啦"},{"pid":"3fb1128b2997e4001f5c3a8a2b419fb9d28bb9c3","tid":1963300,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T07:22:26.000Z","msg":"東方銷量呢？"}]}